        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_DEMOGRAPHICS_METRIC_SETTLEMENT_CAP_PCT_TOOLTIP">
            <Text>Percentage of the settlement cap this player has used. 100% means at the limit.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_DEMOGRAPHICS_METRIC_AGE_PROGRESS">
            <Text>Age Progress</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_DEMOGRAPHICS_METRIC_AGE_PROGRESS_TOOLTIP">
            <Text>How close the current age is to ending. Same for all civilizations.</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_DEMOGRAPHICS_METRIC_CRISIS_STAGE">
            <Text>Crisis Stage</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_DEMOGRAPHICS_METRIC_CRISIS_STAGE_TOOLTIP">
            <Text>Current crisis stage (0 = none, 3 = peak crisis). Game-wide value.</Text>
        </Row>

