        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_DEMOGRAPHICS_METRIC_MILPOWER_TOOLTIP">
            <Text>Summed combat strength across all of this player's military units (land, naval, and air formations).</Text>
        </Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_DEMOGRAPHICS_METRIC_WONDERS">
            <Text>Wonders</Text>
